{
  "id": "adv_event_2308_01_02",
  "title": "彼氏でも\n出来た？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few weeks later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.7066664458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……新曲の振り付け\n難易度高いけど、いい感じになってきたね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant‚ pant‚ pant… The choreography for the new song\nis really tough‚ but it's coming together nicely!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9999996503,
      "endTime": 15.5499996503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。スケジュールはかなり押しているけど\nなんとかフェスには間に合いそうで良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. The schedule is pretty tight‚ but\nit looks like we'll make it in time for the festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7333329837,
      "endTime": 21.683333079100002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん。せやな\n振り付けを変えましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup‚ yup. That's right.\nLet's change the choreography!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8999996503,
      "endTime": 26.590385278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "……って瑠依ちゃんが言うた時は\nそりゃもうびっくりしたけどな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…is what Rui-chan said‚\nand I was so surprised!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7999996503,
      "endTime": 31.1294782003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "もう……悪かったわよ\nでも、せっかく大舞台を任せてもらえるんだもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… I'm sorry.\nBut since we've been given such a big stage‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3333329837,
      "endTime": 37.4800903956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "私達の努力で、少しでもいいものにしたいし\n観に来てくれるみんなを喜ばせたいじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "we want to make it as good as we can with our effort.\nWe want to make everyone who comes to see us happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.666666317,
      "endTime": 44.3189564705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、瑠依ちゃんのそういうところ、うちは好きです\n……ふわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I like that about you‚ Rui-chan.\n…Yawn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5333329837,
      "endTime": 52.524716345499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん、最近あくびが多いね。寝不足？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ you've been yawning a lot lately. Are you tired?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7333329837,
      "endTime": 58.457595984200005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私も気になってたの\nこのところ疲れがとれてないみたいだけど……大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've noticed too.\nYou seem to be really worn out lately… Are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.666666317,
      "endTime": 65.1405440331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "へーき、へーき。全然気にせんといて\n暑さのせいか、ちょっと寝つきが悪いだけやから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine‚ I'm fine. Don't worry 'bout it.\nIt's just the hot weather making it hard to sleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3333329837,
      "endTime": 73.0567114513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "夏バテかな？　美味しい物食べて、スタミナつけよう！\nそろそろ晩ご飯の時間だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it's summer fatigue? Let's eat something good and get our energy up!\nIt's almost dinner time anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.266666317,
      "endTime": 81.4666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、三人で食べに行きましょう\nさくらにお勧めのとんかつ屋さんを教えてもらったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ let's all go out to eat together.\nSakura recommended a great tonkatsu place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.666666317,
      "endTime": 87.94303808219999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "とんかつ！？　やったーっ！　瑠依ちゃんナイス！\n楽しみだね、優ちゃん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tonkatsu!? Yay! Nice one‚ Rui-chan!\nThis will be fun‚ right‚ Yu-chan!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1333329837,
      "endTime": 94.81333309819999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "……今からかぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…From now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9999996503,
      "endTime": 96.7514796813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……悪いんやけど、うち遠慮しとくわ\n今日のところは二人で行ってきて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… I'm sorry‚ but I'll skip this time.\nYou two go ahead without me today‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0333380699,
      "endTime": 104.71333818439999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "え～！？　優ちゃん\n最近、ちっとも私達に付き合ってくれない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Yu-chan!\nLately‚ you never hang out with us anymore!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9000047366,
      "endTime": 111.4200045268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、優の寝不足の原因ってフェスの準備で\n過密スケジュールになってるせい……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that Yu's lack of sleep is because of\nthe festival preparations and the tight schedule…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6333380699,
      "endTime": 118.6167167664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃんに隠し事は出来んなぁ\n実はうち、大舞台を前にして、緊張しとるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui-chan‚ you know me too well.\nActually‚ I'm really nervous about the big stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8333380699,
      "endTime": 126.850231266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、緊張をほぐすためにも\n私達と遊ぶのがいいんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ maybe you should\nhang out with us to relax!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0666714032,
      "endTime": 133.1377147039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんな。このところ用事が重なっててな\n今日も親戚の法事があるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry. I've had a lot of things going on lately.\nI have a family memorial service today too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3333380699,
      "endTime": 140.0333381652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "それ、こないだも言ってたよね。……本当？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said that last time too… Is it really true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2333380699,
      "endTime": 145.35097980499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "本当の本当",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's really true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5666714032,
      "endTime": 147.317124923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "本当の本当の本当？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really‚ really true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5333380699,
      "endTime": 150.2789843559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "本当の本当の本当の本当……\nっていつまで続くん！？　うちのこと疑い過ぎです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really‚ really‚ really true…\nHow long are we gonna keep this up!? Y'all are doubting me too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4666714032,
      "endTime": 158.9466717084,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15099.99512050001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "今度のフェスが終わる頃には一段落してるから\nそしたらいっぱい遊ぼう？　ほな、お先やで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things will calm down after the festival.\nThen we can hang out a lot. Well‚ see y'all later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1333380699,
      "endTime": 166.8768528939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "行っちゃった……\n最近、練習が終わったらすぐ一人で帰っちゃうよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She left…\nRecently‚ she always goes home alone right after practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4666958173,
      "endTime": 175.9904144605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "でもご親戚の法事なら仕方ないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if it's a family memorial service‚ it can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.2000291507,
      "endTime": 180.1000290553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……\n親戚の法事はそんなに連続しないと思うよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…\nFamily memorial services don't happen that often‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.3000291507,
      "endTime": 186.72399727509998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
